<tr border=0 bgcolor="yellow"  bordercolor="white"><td width=50% border=0 valign="top">(03-12-10) Seorang pengawal keselamatan hari ini mengaku bersalah di mahkamah sesyen di Kangar, atas tuduhan merogol anak kandungnya yang berusia 12 tahun sebulan pada 22 November lalu.  Lelaki berusia 38 tahun itu tidak diwakili peguam  dan mengaku bersalah sebaik sahaja pertuduhan dibacakan.  Tertuduh juga telah mengugut mangsa agar tidak memberitahu sesiapa.</td>
<td width=50% border=0 valign="top">A security guard today admitted guilty at a sessions court in Kangar to a charge of raping his own daughter aged 12 years 1 month last 22nd November.  The man aged 38 was not represented by a lawyer and admitted guilty as soon as the charge was read out.  The accused had also threatened the victim not to inform anyone.</td></tr>
